# Binti AI Models

This directory contains the AI models used by Binti voice assistant.

## Model Structure

```
assets/
├── models/
│   ├── wake/
│   │   └── ya_binti_detector.tflite    (5 MB) - Wake word detection
│   ├── asr/
│   │   └── vosk-model-egyptian/        (50 MB) - Egyptian Arabic ASR
│   └── nlu/
│       └── egybert_tiny_int8.tflite    (30 MB) - Intent classification
├── voices/
│   └── ar-EG-female/                   (80 MB) - Egyptian TTS voice
└── commands/
    └── dilink_intent_map.json          - Intent patterns
```

## Downloading Models

Models are downloaded from GitHub Releases on first run:
- User is prompted to download offline models (~160MB total)
- Or can choose cloud-only mode (requires internet)

## Model Sources

| Model | Source | License |
|-------|--------|---------|
| Wake Word | Custom TFLite | MIT |
| ASR | Vosk Egyptian | Apache 2.0 |
| NLU | EgyBERT-tiny | MIT |
| TTS | Coqui TTS | MPL 2.0 |

## Adding Models

1. Build/train your models
2. Quantize to INT8 for mobile
3. Add SHA256 checksum to ModelManager.kt
4. Upload to GitHub Release

---

**Note:** Model files are not included in the repository. Download from Releases.
